  "title": "What Painting I'm Looking At?",
  "description": "Adds unique textures to paintings",
  "body": "### Requires the mod <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/chime\" target=\"_blank\">Chime</a> or Optifine CIT to work!\n\nIn 1.19.4 Mojang added an item for every single painting into the creative tab, but now we have a lot of item wich are the same until you hover over your mouse, and there's a big chance that you don't even know the name of the painting so I made a preview for every single painting!\n\n<a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/bangetto\" target=\"_blank\">\n  \n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/PhaxOHJ2/images/7f63f3bd0aa1dd7b26305bcc0ef629fa2490a1ec.png\">\n  \n  <img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/81c7319d-d963-477b-9ea6-7fb11e1b8a46.webp\">\n  \n</a>\n\n## Supported Mods\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/dark-paintings\" target=\"_blank\">Dark Paintings</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/macaws-paintings\" target=\"_blank\">Macaw's Paintings</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/oakspaintings\" target=\"_blank\">OaksPaintings</a></li>\n</ul>\nYou want your favorite mod to be supported? Suggest it on <a href=\"https://discord.gg/57GdhxYYfd\" target=\"_blank\">Discord</a>!",
